lead_paragraph: For a split second Garbine Muguruza stood wide-eyed and open mouthed as she seemed to have no clue if her lob had landed in -- but as she turned towards the VIP Box, the wild cheers proved she had dethroned Serena Williams to win the French Open title.

headline.print_headline: Muguruza Dethrones Serena Again in Paris to Win French Open
headline.main: Muguruza Dethrones Serena Again in Paris to Win French Open
